node.text:
So y’all know that I hardly ever do ads, but when I find a healing product that I 100% truly believe in, (and has helped with my own healing journey) I NEED to tell you about it! 
〰️
@healthpersonas is a new healthcare company that provides accessible health coaching through video chat with your own personal healer. 
〰️
They have this awesome assessment called the KNOW ME assessment, which helps you to gain valuable insights into your true self including your strengths and areas of improvement.
〰️
Then they connect you with a  health expert that provides you with a deeper understanding of your results!
〰️
My HealthGuide was so knowledgable and she helped me learn so much more about what areas of my life that I’m most motivated by, which is my need for security and meaningful relationships (SO TRUE)!
〰️
It was so cool to see a more in-depth look into what may be lacking in my life and how to focus more on attaining more fulfillment.
〰️
Check out the link in my bio to download the app👉 @theanxietyhealer ....click on 'social media referral' upon checkout, and take the KNOW ME assessment to see what type of results turn up for you! myhealthpersona.com/app
〰️
If you are interested in full access of the app, you can always click on ‘social media referral’ upon checkout and get your first 30 days for only $4.99! Happy healing y’all!
〰️

Photo by The Anxiety Healer on September 06, 2021. May be an image of ‎one or more people and ‎text that says '‎אאאאי To cope with anxiety it's essential to sit down, identify what's worrying you, and address your concerns. When we create daily routines through exercising or changing our sleeping patterns, this allows our bodies to adjust and know what to expect. @theanxietyhealer‎'‎‎.

Photo by The Anxiety Healer on September 06, 2021. May be an image of ‎text that says '‎אי Journaling is a great way to establish a regular schedule, especially for those struggling with anxiety. Journaling at the same time every day can help you starta process-or routine-of mental restoration and wellness. @theanxietyhealer‎'‎.

Photo by The Anxiety Healer on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'No matter how busy you are, there are different ways to create routine. Try making the following changes to your daily schedule: .Stick to a morning routine. @theanxietyhealer •Avoid hitting the snooze button. •Take periodical breaks throughout the day. .Schedule time to be alone. Take note of at least 3 things you're grateful for daily. •Stop work at the same time every day.'.

Photo by The Anxiety Healer on September 06, 2021. May be an image of ‎one or more people and ‎text that says '‎אי Studies have shown that it takes 21 days to form a new habit, and the same goes for a routine. If you set and stick to a new plan for three weeks, there's a good chance you'll stick to the routine for a long time. @theanxietyhealer‎'‎‎.

Why people with Anziet and/or Depression actually cancel plans... waom They're on edge and struggle in situations that's not in their control. They're too exhausted to face the world and pretend they're okay. They're struggling and they don't want to burden you with their problems. Because they need some time alone. Their symptoms have set in.'.

node.text:
I can’t believe how much I can relate too all of these…
〰️
Sometimes my anxiety makes it just too overwhelming for me to stick with I have planned…
〰️
Many times it’s because I’m too exhausted to face the world and pretend that I’m ok…
〰️
Other times it’s because I don’t want to be a burden and I really need to be alone…
〰️
All I know is that when I cancel plans it’s not because I didn’t want to follow through, but it’s because my anxiety is screaming at me that danger is around the corner and I don’t know how to fight it..
〰️
Nowadays, I make plans based on what I want to do and not what others expect of me. I’m a recovering people pleaser so I’m learning how to say NO more often without feeling bad about it. And I’m learning how to set boundaries with myself and others.
〰️
I make plans, but I give myself grace and compassion if I wake up one morning and feel too overwhelmed to follow through.
〰️
The people in your life who support you and love you will understand and not judge you.
〰️
Do you cancel plans often due to your anxiety or depression? Share your experience in the comments ⬇️⬇️⬇️
〰️
Follow 👉 @theanxietyhealer for all things anxiety healing!
〰️

node.text:
How I kicked anxiety in the a** last weekend! Felt like I was at a level 9 as I was driving to meet my friends mostly because I didnt know what to expect…and also bc I knew I would be without a bathroom close by for 2-3 hours (those with IBS will understand this!!)…
〰️
But with a little cognitive restructuring, positive self-talk, healing coping statements, peppermint oil, breathwork, and preparation… I had one of the best days I’ve had in years!
〰️
Maybe that sounds like a lot of prep, but now that I know what I need in my anxiety healing toolkit, I can more easily face my fears and stay away from avoidance! 
〰️
Thank you @bcrivercountry !!!It was honestly so incredibly fun and I felt so proud of myself for doing something outside of my comfort zone and kicking anxiety’s a** ☺️☺️👍👍
〰️
What have you done lately to kick anxiety’s a** ?? Let me know in the comments!
〰️
Follow 👉 @theanxietyhealer for all things anxiety healing!
〰️
